<h1>Appointment Confirmed!</h1>
<p>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</p>
<p>Your appointment has been successfully confirmed with the following details:</p>
<div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px;">
  <p><strong>Provider:</strong> <%= @provider.name %></p>
  <p><strong>Service:</strong> <%= @provider.service_type %></p>
  <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @appointment.start_time.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
  <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @appointment.start_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %></p>
  <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= @provider.location %></p>
</div>
<p>Please make sure to arrive on time. If you need to cancel or reschedule, please contact us as soon as possible.</p>
<p>Best regards,<br>
  Team NearYou</p>
 